        <li><strong>Account data</strong> — retained for as long as your account is active. Deleted within <strong>30 days</strong> of account deletion.</li>
        <li><strong>Quiz history & learning data</strong> — retained for the life of your account. Deleted with your account.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment records</strong> — retained for <strong>10 years</strong> as required by French accounting law (<em>Code de commerce, Art. L123-22</em>). Only transaction references (not card details) are stored by us.</li>
        <li><strong>Server logs (IP addresses)</strong> — retained for a maximum of <strong>12 months</strong> for security purposes.</li>
        <li><strong>Inactive accounts</strong> — accounts with no login for <strong>24 consecutive months</strong> may be deleted after prior email notice.</li>
      </ul>
